channel.title: Runefx With fixed client
channel.description:
Yeah well, Rash gave me permission to release a fixed client for runefx. Original Thread. [quote="Rash, post:1, topic:375582"]Releasing it, its nothing really. Yea, its a PI.
Server & Client Bundle Updated with memory leak fixes and crashes! [b]Credits[/b] Sanity Whoever made iHybrid, i think it was Aintaro
[b]Features[/b] 525 Graphics Great Economy Incredible donator benefits (cant be bothered listing) New home Autocasting works Clan chat works Pming works New HP bars New curses, 100% with emotes (not against npc's) Skillcape Emotes All specs work 100% Teleports Revised, much better now Lunar spell book works. Corporeal Beast Tormented Demons Full GWD JAD Chaos elemental New items Warriors Guild Chaotics New items
[b]Pictures[/b] Watch video for most of the features.
[url=http://www.youtube.com/v/G-GphnBOcCk?fs=1&hl=en_US&color1=0x006699&color2=0x54abd6]Video HERE[/url]
[img]http://i51.tinypic.com/2q8584n.jpg[/img] [img]http://i51.tinypic.com/sdegkw.png[/img] [img]http://i55.tinypic.com/okzqrt.png[/img] [img]http://i55.tinypic.com/n3m2wh.png[/img] [img]http://i52.tinypic.com/2zp2zo0.png[/img] [img]http://i51.tinypic.com/1zquh3n.png[/img] [img]http://i55.tinypic.com/vr6nmt.png[/img] [img]http://i52.tinypic.com/11l4pbr.png[/img]
Ive been hosting this for a while, but im moving on, so thought id release.
[b]Links[/b] http://dl.dropbox.com/u/17253701/DSPK.rar < Cache http://dl.dropbox.com/u/17253701/runefdx.rar < Source.[/quote] Fixed client, http://uppit.com/xl12ogs9qzs4/Runefx_Fixed_Clientr.rar
None of this is mine, all i did was fix the cache re uploaded it, And fixed auto cache. If you have any problems, Please post. also No credits to me
